Package: rforceplots
Type: Package
Title: Additive Force Plots based on SHAP and shapjs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Rafael", "Henkin",
                    email = "r.henkin@qmul.ac.uk", 
                    role = c("aut", "cre")),
            person("Scott", "Lundberg", role = c("ctb","cph"), comment = "shapjs package" )
            )
Maintainer: Rafael Henkin <r.henkin@qmul.ac.uk>
Description: The package is a stand-alone wrapper for the shapjs package to facilitate rendering additive force plots in R.
  Besides a single user-friendly function for plotting and Shiny bindings, the package also exports the three base visualisation functions from shapjs.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
